Children, part of a group of 87 Central American migrants deported from the US, wait at the El Chaparral border crossing before being transported to a shelter in Tijuana, Mexico, on Monday.  According to Mexican Foreign Minister Marcelo Ebrard, Mexican and US authorities will meet in 45 days in Washington. Photo: AFP  
